# CI/CD Standards

Projects must support **dual CI/CD environments**:

GitHub Actions  
Azure DevOps

---

## Pipeline Requirements

Pipelines must:

- Restore dependencies
- Build projects
- Run tests
- Produce artifacts

---

## Build Validation

Every pull request must trigger:

Build  
Unit tests  
Static analysis

PRs must not be merged if builds fail.

---

## Branch Strategy

Use feature branches.

Example:

feature/PROJ-123-user-deactivation

Pull requests must reference the traceable work item when your process requires it.

---

## Deployment

Deployments must be automated.

Stages:

Build  
Test  
Deploy

---

## Artifact Management

Build artifacts must be versioned.

Avoid rebuilding identical artifacts for each environment.

---

## Security

Secrets must not be stored in source code.

Use:

GitHub Secrets  
Azure Key Vault